'''猶他佩森聖殿'''（Payson Utah Temple）是一座位於[[猶他州|猶他州]][[佩森_(猶他州)|佩森]]的[[耶穌基督後期聖徒教會|耶穌基督後期聖徒教會]]聖殿。佩森聖殿在2010年宣布修建，是猶他州的第15座耶穌基督後期聖徒教會聖殿<ref>{{citation |url= http://www.mormonnewsroom.org/ldsnewsroom/eng/news-releases-stories/president-monson-announces-new-temple-in-payson-utah |title= President Monson Announces New Temple in Payson, Utah |work= Newsroom |publisher= LDS Church |date= January 25, 2010 |accessdate= 2012-11-06 |archive-date= 2019-02-16 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20190216095905/https://www.mormonnewsroom.org/ldsnewsroom/eng/news-releases-stories/president-monson-announces-new-temple-in-payson-utah |dead-url= no }}</ref>。2015年，猶他佩森聖殿竣工<ref>{{citation |first= Donald W. |last= Meyers |date= October 18, 2011 |title= Mormons break ground for Payson Temple |url= http://www.sltrib.com/sltrib/news/52694330-183/temple-church-construction-oaks.html.csp |newspaper= [[The_Salt_Lake_Tribune|The Salt Lake Tribune]] |accessdate= 2012-11-06 |archive-date= 2016-10-22 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20161022092538/http://www.sltrib.com/sltrib/news/52694330-183/temple-church-construction-oaks.html.csp |dead-url= no }}</ref><ref name="#1">Compare with the 1996 [[Mount_Timpanogos_Utah_Temple|Mount Timpanogos Utah Temple]] at 107,240 sq ft on a 16.7 acre lot</ref>。

這座聖殿於2015年建立。教會總會會長多馬·孟森會長（Thomas S. Monson）於2010年1月25日宣布其建造。該聖殿位於[[佩森_(猶他州)|佩森]]的西930號路和南1550號路的交叉點附近，在之前未開發的土地上。在宣布之時，尚無其他細節，例如聖殿的計劃大小。<ref>{{citation |url= https://newsroom.churchofjesuschrist.org/ldsnewsroom/eng/news-releases-stories/president-monson-announces-new-temple-in-payson-utah |title= President Monson Announces New Temple in Payson, Utah |work= Newsroom |publisher= LDS Church |date= January 25, 2010 |accessdate= November 6, 2012 |archive-date= 2021-04-18 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20210418071518/https://newsroom.churchofjesuschrist.org/ldsnewsroom/eng/news-releases-stories/president-monson-announces-new-temple-in-payson-utah |dead-url= no }}</ref>

達林·烏克司長老（Dallin H.Oaks）於2011年10月8日主持了奠基儀式，威廉·沃克長老（William R. Walker）指揮，史帝文‧舒長老（Steven E. Snow），傑伊·詹森長老（Jay E. Jensen）和珍妮特·貝克漢姆姐妹（Janette Hales Beckham）出席了開幕式。傑森·查菲茲（Jason Chaffetz）（代表佩森（Payson）在內的猶他州第三國會區代表）參加了鏟土儀式。<ref>{{citation |first= R. Scott |last= Lloyd |date= October 8, 2011 |title= Payson Utah Temple groundbreaking - a temple stands as a lighted beacon |url= https://www.thechurchnews.com/archive/2011-10-08/payson-utah-temple-groundbreaking-a-temple-stands-as-a-lighted-beacon-37658 |newspaper= [[Church_News|Church News]] |accessdate= November 6, 2012 }}</ref><ref>{{citation |first= Rena |last= Lesué-Smithey |date= October 9, 2011 |title= Authorities break ground for new LDS temple in Payson |url= http://www.heraldextra.com/news/local/south/payson/article_bda1dd49-4d9f-5bda-8ef1-4f49f99c3721.html |newspaper= [[Daily_Herald_(Utah)|Daily Herald]] |location= Utah |accessdate= November 6, 2012 |archive-date= 2021-04-16 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20210416180141/https://www.heraldextra.com/news/local/south/payson/article_bda1dd49-4d9f-5bda-8ef1-4f49f99c3721.html |dead-url= no }}</ref>

2015年竣工後，這座聖殿成為近幾年來最大的建築之一，佔地15英畝（6公頃），面積96,630平方英尺（8977平方公尺）。2015年4月24日至5月23日，不包括星期日，舉行了公開參觀。[8]這座聖殿是亨利·艾寧（Henry B. Eyring）在2015年6月7日奉獻的。<ref>{{citation |first= Donald W. |last= Meyers |date= October 18, 2011 |title= Mormons break ground for Payson Temple |url= http://www.sltrib.com/sltrib/news/52694330-183/temple-church-construction-oaks.html.csp |newspaper= [[The_Salt_Lake_Tribune|The Salt Lake Tribune]] |accessdate= November 6, 2012 |archive-date= 2016-10-22 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20161022092538/http://www.sltrib.com/sltrib/news/52694330-183/temple-church-construction-oaks.html.csp |dead-url= no }}</ref><ref name="#1"/> <ref>{{citation |url= https://newsroom.churchofjesuschrist.org/article/new-temples-to-open-in-2015 |title= New Temples To Open in 2015 |work= Newsroom |publisher= [[LDS_Church|LDS Church]] |date= December 12, 2014 |accessdate= 2021-04-15 |archive-date= 2021-04-18 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20210418112924/https://newsroom.churchofjesuschrist.org/article/new-temples-to-open-in-2015 |dead-url= no }}</ref><ref name="Dedication-payson" />

2020年，因冠狀病毒大流行而關閉了佩森猶他聖殿。<ref>Stack, Peggy Fletcher. [https://www.sltrib.com/religion/2020/03/26/all-latter-day-saint/ "All Latter-day Saint temples to close due to coronavirus"] {{Wayback|url=https://www.sltrib.com/religion/2020/03/26/all-latter-day-saint/ |date=20200818145648 }}, ''[[The_Salt_Lake_Tribune|The Salt Lake Tribune]]'', 26 March 2020. Retrieved on 28 March 2020.</ref>

